    "description": {
      "value": "<h2>Missionary</h2><p>Missionaries are emissaries of the Emperor's divine light and carriers of the burning flames of righteous hatred. They spread the Imperial Creed to the far reaches of the galaxy, converting the masses and purging the taint of heresy wherever they find it. Through fire and faith, they inspire ordinary men to acts of extraordinary courage, turning rabble into zealots who will gladly die for the God-Emperor.</p><h3>Starting Skills</h3><p>Common Lore (Imperial Creed, Imperium) (Int), Forbidden Lore (Heresy) (Int), Medicae (Int), Scholastic Lore (Imperial Creed) (Int), Speak Language (High Gothic, Low Gothic) (Int)</p><h3>Starting Talents</h3><p>Basic Weapon Training (Universal), Melee Weapon Training (Universal), Pure Faith, Unshakeable Faith</p><h3>Starting Gear</h3><p>Good-craftsmanship chainsword or best-craftsmanship staff, good-craftsmanship flamer or best-craftsmanship lasgun, best-craftsmanship guard flak armour, Ecclesiarchal robes, aquila pendant, sepulchre, censer and incense, micro-bead.</p><h3>Special Ability</h3><p><strong>Pure Faith:</strong> The Missionary begins play with the Pure Faith Talent. See page 104 for more details.</p>"
    },
